parameters: Chancellor: Knight, step forward.
Yes, sir!

Chancellor: As you may know, our kingdom is currently
planning a large-scale expedition to subdue monsters in the
west.

Chancellor: This time, our queen, who has succeeded the
throne from the previous king, will also accompany the
expedition.
That is quite...!
Chancellor: Let me continue.

Chancellor: Of course, she will not be going to the front
lines to fight. However, it is not hard to imagine that the
march will be arduous. What we expect is a decrease in
morale among the troops, leading to a reduction in combat
effectiveness.

Chancellor: However, by having the queen herself present to
inspire them, she will become a pillar of mental support for
the soldiers and will surely boost their morale.

Chancellor: She has decided to fulfill this symbolic role
herself this time.
Indeed, Her Majesty is most noble.
Chancellor: However, there is a problem.

Chancellor: It is that the succession of the throne from the
late king to the current queen was an urgent affair due to
his death in battle, and it has not been long since then.

Chancellor: While we are preparing for the expedition,
unfortunately, there are still many among the troops who are
hesitant about whether she is truly a sovereign worthy of
their lives.
How utterly disrespectful...!

Queen: It is my lack of power that is to blame. Do not think
ill of those who serve.

The queen should not say such things. If only we had more
strength to support you, such disrespect would never be
tolerated...

Chancellor: Mere lamentation is not a talent. If we change
our perspective, we can say that the issues needing
resolution have been narrowed down.

Chancellor: A symbol must be made fitting through
appropriate design, indeed.

Chancellor: Therefore, I have summoned you here today to
command you to search for the sacred banner and treasure
sword to be carried by the princess during her military
campaigns.

Chancellor: The blade's radiance is said to house the light
of dawn, a supreme treasure within the royal family's
legends. "The Sword of Dawn," I want you to search for it
and bring it back.
──...!! The Sword of Dawn, you say...!?
Chancellor: What's the matter? Do you have a complaint?
No, not at all! It's just that...

An exceedingly important mission, I shall certainly bring it
back...!

Chancellor: Do not rush, I am not imposing an impossible
task on you.

Chancellor: As you well know, the treasure sword was lost
amidst the chaos of a distant past, and its whereabouts are
now unknown.

Chancellor: I am not mistaken in your loyalty to command you
to bring back something that exists only in legend.

Chancellor: Rather, it is precisely because you are a person
of deep trust with the king that I wish to entrust this task
to you this time.
Chancellor: You understand what I mean?

Chancellor: Just now, someone captured in the capital turned
out to be from a rare frontier origin.

Chancellor: I thought perhaps we could learn something of
the circumstances of lands seldom heard from, so I took the
opportunity to listen to his story, and there was some
information that caught my attention.

Chancellor: In the depths of the frontier's man-eating cave,
there lies a "Sword of Radiance" that one day drifted there
and still sleeps in that place, a sword without equal in
this world.

Chancellor: If the lost royal treasure were to be in our
hands, who would doubt that we have a king worthy of trust?

Chancellor: First, travel to that land for information
gathering, verify the truth, and if possible, swiftly
recover the treasure sword.

Chancellor: This is an urgent command and one that I want
you to carry out in secrecy. Can I count on you?

Princess: I am aware that I am asking you to take on a
difficult position, but I ask you nonetheless.
00_st_pri_01

Princess: The radiance of the treasure sword is said to lead
the country to dawn. Now more than ever, as my power falls
short and we are in the darkness of chaos, that light is
needed for our country.
00_st_pri_01
Princess: Knight Reisha. I am counting on your valor.

The adventure is a knight's honor! Knight Reisha, I swear
upon my life to live up to your expectations splendidly!!
00_st_pri_01
Princess: I am counting on you, my knight...
